  "text": "We further study the critical behaviors of various measures in the networks with two-scale community structures, a generalization of the single-scale networks (Fig. 1B) . In the networks, the critical r-value of Sq can be estimated by (see SI for the proof), ⁎ r 2 -value is mainly determined by p out1 /p in ; also, equation [CITATION_1] has similar behaviors (see Fig. S6 ). See SI for detailed analysis of critical behaviors of various measures in the networks. We provided a systematical comparison of phase diagrams of various measures (Sq, Sp, Sg and Mod) in the networks (See Figs 4D, S5 and S6) .",
